Build from: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSCourrier/trunk@48908

Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Subject widget on mail view page now comes with its label in a <h4>
- Auto handle at creation time for Incoming Paper Mail
- Injection portlet (visible for global injector across the portal)
- mail from and to linked to specific directories in paper setup:
  local_addressbook for mailbox level contacts
  addressbook for global contacts
  groups for internal recipients
- mailboxes local roles are mapped to corresponding entry
  local roles in local_addressbook
