** CPSCourrier V0.15.0 [R1 build 2006/06/21-17:05 by gracinet]
** SVN URL: https://svn.nuxeo.org/pub/CPS3/products/CPSCourrier/trunk Revision: 46692
Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- specific factory for CPSCourrier and its options
