- fix batch perform view bug on session expiration
- DGME #4461: the local managers and supervisors no longer can trigger
  stack protected transitions directly (but they can still manage the stack
  itself)
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Mailbox filter uses tree cache for its voc. Much faster
- [OPTIM]: batch perform now commits for each wf transition to avoid sending
  emails while the proxy remain in the previous state

